metadata.name: ST-G4-EH#1
metadata.description:
ST-G4-EH#1 - 4th Generation of Sentient Trash: Electric Hobo #1

Electric Hobos is a 1/1 collection hand drawn by Sirius Crocodile. The NFT gives access to the a PFP file and a collection of high-res wallpapers and banners.

---  
A trash planet of the Terra Konscia system turned sentient. Layers upon layers of electronic waste and computer chips have started to amalgamate and reorganize, following command issued by discarded AI models. Electric Hobos are one of artificial species resulting from the self-initiated self-learning process.
